        <num>20-2-1111</num>
        <content>
          <p>During any school year, a school bus driver may utilize up to a maximum of three days of any accumulated sick leave for the purpose of absenting himself from his duties for any personal reason if prior approval of his absence is given by the local school superintendent or his authorized representative.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1972, p. 488, ยง 1.)</p>
